<plot>The Fallon lumber company is after California's redwood trees but logger Bill Cardigan who wants to save the trees is in the way. Cardigan has a note due at the bank and needs to get a large supply of logs to the mill. He sends his logs down the river so Fallon builds a dam to stop him. As Cardigan sets dynamite to blow up the dam, Fallon arrives to stop him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?617772</url></doc>
